# Copy to .dev.vars (not committed) — wrangler local dev secrets
# Used by CF Pages Functions when running `wrangler pages dev` or `npm run dev`.
#
# Production/Preview equivalents live in:
# Cloudflare Dashboard → Pages → trip-planner → Settings → Environment variables

# Mapbox Directions API token (public pk.* token, for /api/route proxy)
# Get one free at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.ey...your-token-here

# Mock Auth — 本機開發 bypass Cloudflare Access
# 設定後，wrangler 的 middleware 會假裝此 email 已登入，讓 /manage/、/admin/、寫入 API 可用
# 不設 → 本機打 /api/my-trips 會拿到 401，/manage 看到「無法存取」
ADMIN_EMAIL=your-email@example.com
DEV_MOCK_EMAIL=your-email@example.com

# OpenRouteService API key — 路徑/車程計算（POST /trips/:id/recompute-travel）
# 註冊免費（2,000 req/day, 40 req/min）：https://openrouteservice.org/dev/#/signup
ORS_API_KEY=eyJvcmci...your-token

# OpenTripMap API key — POI rating + 補欄位（OSM + Wikidata 包裝）
# 註冊免費（5,000 req/day, 5 req/sec）：https://opentripmap.io/product
OPENTRIPMAP_API_KEY=your-opentripmap-key

# === 2026-05-02 email cutover (Mac mini Gmail SMTP via Tailscale Funnel) ===
# CF Pages Functions 透過 ${TRIPLINE_API_URL}/internal/mail/send 走 mac mini，
# 由 mac mini scripts/tripline-api-server.ts 用 nodemailer + Gmail SMTP 寄出。
# 取代 RESEND_API_KEY（已棄用）。

# Mac mini Gmail SMTP credentials（在 mac mini .env.local 設，不是 wrangler）
# - 從 GitHub Actions secrets 複用同一組（daily-report.yml 已用），少一組密碼管
# - App Password 不是 Gmail 登入密碼，需在 https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords 建立
GMAIL_USERNAME=your-gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
EMAIL_FROM=Tripline <your-gmail@gmail.com>

# Telegram admin alert（CF Pages 端用，silent-skip 改 audit + alert 後失敗會通知）
# 複用 scripts/daily-check 的同一組 token + chat_id
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=

# === poi-favorites-rename §18.1-18.2 (companion path) ===
# OAuth client_credentials access_token used by mac mini cron tp-request scheduler
# to call /api/poi-favorites with companion scope. Mint via:
#   curl -X POST https://trip-planner-dby.pages.dev/api/oauth/token \
#     -d "grant_type=client_credentials" \
#     -d "client_id=tripline-internal-cli" \
#     -d "client_secret=<provisioned-secret>"
# Response includes admin+companion scopes; access_token expires per OAuth spec.
# TRIPLINE_API_TOKEN=local-dev-stub-token

# OAuth client_id used by middleware companion gate to verify the calling client is
# the mac mini cron scheduler (third companion gate after X-Request-Scope header +
# token's companion scope). Required by functions/api/_companion.ts.
# TP_REQUEST_CLIENT_ID=local-dev-mac-mini-cron
